content.detailedDescription: At 7 pm last night i was in my backyard with my cat and i just happened to catch something out of the corner of my eye moving in the nights sky. what i noticed right away was that this object didnt have any lights on, like an airplane would have. what i could see was a sort of glow on the underside of the object that sort of looked like a reflection from the moonlight or sun that had just set an hour ago. i could see 3 small circles in  a triangle pattern. at first the lights were stationary as it moved but then i noticed the 3 circles started rotating in a circle, then the lights started moving in a sort of figure 8 pattern moving in and out of eachother. as this object flew across the sky in a total of 30 seconds time. that is when i knew i had just seen something different.  i have lived under the landing path of lax for 30 years. in the times i've watch countless airplanes come in for landings. and what i saw was no airplane. in fact the object was moving in the exact opposite direction of the airplanes that were coming in for landings at the time . but the object i saw was way above the airplanes. at like satellite height.
content.summary: Saw something flying in the sky at night with no lights. had a strange glow on the bottom with 3 circular lights in a triangle pattern. lights rotated and moved in and out of eachother.

content.detailedDescription: One night when i was nine yrs old we noticed a red light above our barn. it didn't move, blink or change colors. it was there all night every night for four nights. on the fourth night my father saw a single light, he thought it was a headlight from a snowmobile, in the corn field. being january that would have been possible. the next day my father and brother went to the area where the"headlight" was seen and could find no tracks from any kind of vehicle. there had been no new snowfall or heavy winds to erase any tracks that might have been there. around that same time there was a cigar shaped ufo spotted in the area of black river falls wi. my father saw this as he was driving home from work on interstate 90. i believe this was reported in the media but since it was 40 plus yrs ago, and i was a child, i can not remember exact dates to do any kind of research on it. we never felt any fear from the lights and after the 4th night it vanished and nothing was seen again. i have never had another experience but am curious as to what these lights could have been.
content.summary: Red light appeared for four nights above a barn, stayed stationary. single light seen on ground in the corn field on first night. of red light.

content.detailedDescription: I exited the freeway. headed west and stopped at a stoplight. i was signaling to turn left. in front of me in the night sky is a reddish-glowing, star-like object. i asked myself what it was. i pulled over to the side once i turned left. the object released a flash of light that looked like a strand. then a pulsating object appeared below it and descended. it disappeared and the star-like object looked stationary but it quickly disappeared into space. in my mind that was a ufo. so many questions are running on my mind as i type this. the government has to know something and why is it that they're not telling us.
content.summary: Starlike. ejected an object that was pulsating.

content.detailedDescription: It hovered over the skylines of my neighbors house and i lost it through some tree tops it was a cigar shaped with a dome on the top i saw some squares on the dome that were way too big for an airplane it covered with no sound with a strange white glow it was a good football field maybe 2 size i honestly didn't feel much of a reaction i'm a strong believer in ufos but this is the first time i've ever had an encounter i was in my backyard smoking a cigarette staring off into the distance and this object ufo came into my peripherals it i lost the object or the ufo whatever it was through some tree tops i try to go around trees but it was gone

content.detailedDescription: I was just leaving a friends house when i saw a glowing orange/copper fireball like object approximately 1/4 of a mile away in the sky heading to the n/nw not making a sound and i got my friend to come out and see it and we both watched it as it headed directly towards us then changed direction heading w and then changing direction heading sw as it slowly faded but was visible until i lost sight of it when it dropped below the horizon. this all happens right over joint base lewis mccord in tacoma, wa. i have lived here my entire 52 years and know airplanes and this was no airplane. left my quite shaken. the joint base lewis mccord people must have tracked it because it was in their airspace. i video'd part of the event with my phone camera but it is not very good and was hard to track with me shaking
content.summary: Saw glowing object coming from se moving slowly towards nw noisless changed direction going w then going to sw

content.detailedDescription:
I was on an apartment building rooftop six stories above street level, enjoying the night scene of city lights/buildings and traffic below.
a movement above my head caught my attention.
i first thought it was a huge bird of some sort, such as a crane.
the reason i thought it was a crane or huge type of bird is that the object's wings resembled a bird's wings in general shape and there was no sound. 
i realized my mistake when i saw small white lights rimming the perimeter of each wing, one wing on the left, one on the right, and they were stationary. the object was so dark/black and non-reflective that the other parts of it not defined by lights were blended with the darkness of the night sky. the weather was calm and quiet.
the object flew in a straight line and i watched it as long as i could, but as it approached the horizon, it seemed to disappear. there were other aircraft in the sky at the time - at least one airplane and a helicopter in the far distance. i thought that surely the pilots of the helicopter and airplane would be able to notice the dark craft, as it seemed to be heading into their airspace.
it could have been a stealth military plane, i suppose. i don't believe it could have been a drone. it was very large to my perspective and absolutely silent, and there was no detectable smell of fuel. had it not been for seeing the movement of the lights passing overhead, i may not have noticed it at all.
content.summary: Object flew silently overhead and seemed to disappear.

content.detailedDescription: In the last week of march 2011 i was relaxing at home smoking a cig after a small meal when i notice a bright object in the sky over newark airport nj. at first i studied the object and observe closely because of its brightness. i was expecting a plane. what i saw was a large orb in a circular shape and extremely bright acting in a bobbing motion and what it seem to do was move in a very short distance fast. i thought it was a plane at first but it's speed and movements planes can not do.It was to big and to bright. it then moved a short distance further north and closer to manhattan in the sky of 14th street and the hudson river. its movements were unlike any plane i see fly at night. bobbing at times and at times staying completely still. no sound what so ever. i was a little excited but focused enough to realize this is something i have never experienced before. i live in a 24 story building with an open view of lower manhattan east to west skyline. my windows face approx 270 degrees south west. i can view the open skies over newark airport n j and lower manhattans hudson river. 14th street east to west view. i asked my friend who was standing behind me to view this light and its large bright circular orb shape. it seem like it was completely still. no sooner then i asked him what can it be it moved straight up counter clockwise and stopped at ten o'clock. it moved in a large space of the sky in a moment. to describe this in seconds is to much time. that's right, it made a large question mark in reverse in the sky of nj. what seem like just over the sky of 14th street hudson river. i was jumping in my apartment realizing i had no recording device. it was parked at 10 o'clock bobbing slightly. it then moved from 10 o'clock to 5 o'clock releasing a ashy light before stopping. this ashy light glowed and slowly faded into the clear no cloud sky. at this point it started to move like a stone skipping on water moving very fast going east toward long island. it came over west 14th street toward east 14th street' over the east river toward brooklyn and all the way out toward long island. i lost sight of this ufo as it passed directly over my window. i got a excellent close up view as it passed my window going east. my windows face west only. the duration of this experience lasted about 3 to 5 minutes wide awake with company. i know what i saw.
content.summary: A friend and myself observed a orb over the skies of newark n j airport and lower manhattan hudson river area

content.detailedDescription: Walking dog-partial clear sky (clouds rolling by-windy)- i always look up-as i love astronomy-i see what i think is a star (very bright, almost pulsating)- at about 45degrees facing east, venus?-it had fuzzy edges (to me)- and rear facing "arm like appendages" on top. i let dog in and asked wife and daughter to get shoes on and come out to help me clarify what the heck i am seeing?-they see it also. i took cell phone video, with audio description of what we are "seeing". i ran in to get binoculars-this is where it gets weird-the craft is dinner plate shaped with "indented like pie plate" look to it. the "arms" i  though i saw was actually the craft turning up on it's side while hovering (total 51 minute of observation (intermittent because of clouds rolling by-very windy here tonight).Big dipper on my left upper, orion on my right rear upper, and near full moon just up east in tree tops. at least 10 other jets, planes going by in different directions (we have airport 3 miles away-and major airports within one hour or three hours from here)-this thing defies anything i've ever seen anything do on a very windy night-up in the sky. we felt awe, and my wife was unnerved, my daughter a little of both, as myself. lost sight when stars now obscured by clouds.
content.summary: "dinner plate"shape resembles "ferris wheel" red and green coencentric circular red and green lights with white ,short apendages sticking out. craft rotated and then flat again contantly.

content.detailedDescription: I have seen this specific ufo several times in my life. but this experience was very personal. the ufo appeared suddenly in the sky, my girlfriend could see it too it followed us for about twelve miles then it began to get very close. i don't know how to describe it the craft or being was then inside of the car inside of us almost. my car almost felt pushed alnoing the road as well. i was traveling to my friends house and as we pulled in her drive it came to the top of the trees my friend was also able to see it very clearly. on the way out of her driveway it was blocked b several large black vehciles with flashing lights they were turning people around idk exactly what there business was but i took another road home. the light then appeared over a church apparently there was a service that night. i stoped to ask a church goer about the light and the church did indeedhave a spot lightbehind it in the back of a white pickup. i don't think this was a religious experience or anything undeniably a ufo since it followed us through two countys. i wright this now just having expeinced it an hour ago. i almost feel like it was probing us whathing i still have cold chills. i made videos that i will send soon

content.detailedDescription:
In the night sky over nw oklahoma, we saw about a dozen flashing multi-color lights grouped together in the night sky  very far away.
we first saw it peripherally, and then stared at it for further observation.
at first, we thought is was a cluster of stars, but it was uncharacteristic of stars. 
there was a bright white light in the center with green, blue, red, and white lights emanating from it. 
the cluster and center light remained stationary, with the other lights moving toward and away from the white center light.
the cluster remained for over 30 minutes, during which time we recruited two other observers in the neighborhood.
content.summary: Stationary cluster of bright lights at high altitude in the night sky

content.detailedDescription: I went outside to the back deck to take pictures of an incoming storm to the west.  i turned to take some pictures of the sky to the east which was more calm.  i took about 100 pictures using a sony digital camera. i did not notice anything out of the ordinary so i went back inside and downloaded the images to my laptop. i was showing the pictures to my daughter, and immediately she noticed several frames had transparent, triangle shaped images.  they were not cloud-shaped triangles but rather very distinct, triangle/tetrahedral shapes that looked the same color of the sky.  i am attaching one of the images that i did only minor enhancements to, such as reversing the image to negative so that the blue sky appears brighter and the white clouds appear darker.  then i colorized the image.  i have about 12 images with the triangles in them, the original digital copies.  the one attached shows what could be three triangles, in a group, and possibly four-sided, such as a tetrahedron.  closer look shows light or white areas on the triangles which could be windows.  there is a dark area to the upper right of the image that looks like a face, but that is just the reverse value of the clouds.
content.summary: Taking pictures outside of sky.  downloaded to computer and noticed triangles on several images.

content.detailedDescription: I woke up in the middle of the night coughing. it woke up my husband and he asked me if i was ok. i answered "yes i am ok,just coughing". i then went to use the washroom and decided to sit on the couch and opened the window just a crack to have a smoke. it was 3:48 am. while i was sitting there a flash of light came out of the corner of my eye so i looked out the window. i have no doubt there was a ufo above my neighbours house. that house is a bed and breakfast and very tall.  the ufo was bigger than the house and hovering very low over the roof. it had a gold-ish light on it and was circular. i was stunned because i have never witnessed a obvious ufo before let alone one that close. i got an erie feeling and sort of felt frozen. my husband is always talking about aliens and ufo's and i love to listen but really was a non-believer. the object hovered over the house and a beam came down onto the house. both motion lights on the house came on. i tired to see if i could see anything on the ground but could not. i looked at it for about another 30 seconds and then pondered a bit more wondering if i should wake my husband up to see it. i decided i would so i went into the room and whispered his name about 5 times and said i had seen a ufo outside. he finally woke enough to realize i was not joking and came to the window to look. no kidding it was gone (but the neighbours outdoor motion lights were still on. we watched for about another 15 minutes and it did not return so we went back to bed. my reaction to the entire situation is i am no longer a skeptic. this was right there so close before my eyes. i have no doubt in what it was.
content.summary: Ufo hovering over neighbours home, then sent a light beam down onto neighbours house causing motion sensor lights to come on

content.detailedDescription:
I was with my girlfriend visiting irazu volcano national park in cartago costa rica. the weather was really nice. very good sun light not cloudy. this volcano is 3400 mts of altitude above sea level close to the biosphere . so we were above the clouds. like when you fly on airplane. the sky was really clear so at 11:00 am on that altitude part of the sky was light black.We were taking pictures of the volcano and the landscape. the clouds looked like a white sea but i noticed close to one of the mountains some clouds with different forms. so i started to take pictures there. once we finish the tour we headed back home. while i was checking the pictures i noticed one black circle above the mountains i noticed before. it looked like a circular sauce with 2 little antenas one on the top of it and like one on it's tail. on the moment while taking the pictures i did not see it. i took the pictures in a burst. on one pic you can see the object completely clear on the next one vanished. almost in seconds. all the pictures have less than one minute difference. 

i will attach the pictures guys. thanks for your time.

greetings from costa rica.
content.summary: Really clear flying object in costa rican volcano(irazu)

content.detailedDescription:
Location of sighting: bearsted nr maidstone kent england
date of sighting: winter 1968
time: 7.15pm
my age at the time  17 years
i was walking alone from my then home in birling avenue to the bus stop on the main ashford road when an unusual noise attracted my attention- it sounded like the noise you get if you suck air in through clenched teeth – i glanced in the direction it came from and coming towards me very slowly( from the south) at a height lower than house top level i saw a cylindrically shaped craft slightly pointed at each end and illuminated but not really giving off any light. the light was similar to a flourescent light-solid  white and bright. no markings or any other sort of embellishment on it at all. it moved slowly and as i stood still looking up at it it just cruised slowly over me at a height of i would guess maybe 15-20ft. i watched it slowly continuing on its way over the tree tops and the garages and heading away from me in the direction of detling (north) 
(i looked on a map years later and wondered if it might have been heading towards coldblow lane in detling where at the time there was an early warning station- coldblow ace high relay station) which would have had monitoring equipment but is now no longer there). 
at that point i had been watching utterly transfixed and astonished to see something like that-i suddenly felt rather afraid and started to run up fauchons lane (east) then into the landway (headed south)hurrying to the busier ashford road where the bus stop was. as i neared the end of the road i wondered if anything would still be seen of the craft behind me in the distance- as i looked over my right shoulder to take a look i was horrified to find it literally directly above me no more than 15-20ft high -  but this time it was totally silent.I was shocked- i guess it must have followed me as i ran down the road. i was so afraid that i just ran out into the main road- where thankfully there was not a single car in sight which in itself was amazing as this is usually a really busy trunk road but it was strangely empty until after this event.. i ran into the bus shelter and continued watching this craft as it just remained still over the road junction- there was a pub opposite but i was afraid to come out of the bus shelter to go there for help. then 2 young men came out and went into the car park. they tried to start up their motorbike but it wouldnt start( i dont know if this was connected) i looked at them and then back at the object, then as i was watching it it just seemed to ‘switch off’ like a light- if it flew away it was too fast for my eyes to follow it.Some minutes later my bus arrived and i was so shaky i couldn't open my purse to get out my fare and the conductress had to help me. i was so shaken by it that for a long time i didnt tell anyone about it except for my father-although shocked  by this event however, i somehow felt as though i had been 'allowed' to see this- i'm sorry i cant explain it any clearer than that- looking back i dont feel that any harm was intended and that it was more curiosity on the part of the object  watching and observing me. i cannot say if there were any physical effects afterwards as i would not have been knowledgable enough to have associated anything with this sighting but i dont recall any.
 that was my first experience but in subsequent years i have seen and also heard  what i believe to be  things connected with the ufo phemomena including a possible time loss. in almost every house i have lived in since there has been some sort of ufo episode which has also included my son, daughter and husband. i will submit details of further experiences should you require any
content.summary: Saw object came overhead appeared to go north i ran east then south looked to see if there at it was directly overhead

content.detailedDescription: I was in earhart indiana on june 12 2015 at 6:30pm ne spending time at my girls house having a bonfire it was a cold night out so we went inside she went inside for awhile to get warmed up but she said she would come back out after a while so i went back out and attended the bonfire and then i started looking up in the sky because i am a sky n night watcher and then my girl came back out n caught some more fresh air n was seeing what i was doing and then it happen 5 to 7 fly objects started shooting in to the sky 3 shot up in a line n then broke off in a triangle form then a couple feet away 2more shot up then same way an then 2 more in the same area the first 3 took off from shot off as well but the last 2 must of connected in the sky about 100ft up or so n then came falling back to earth in a fiery ball of flame all but one shot off in to the stars/space the crafts were about 1 to 3 miles from us. i was so upset cuz i had no camera on me at the time thou i was super happy i had something like that happened i was witnessing something i strive to see. so i dont got any proof but what my girl eyes n my eyes seen. they were behind some trees so i was a lil unhappy that i couldnt see as clear as i wanted to but i told my girl when we seen the craft started to come down that i could run to it n not care if my lungs burned cuz i was so excited to see that.. i will never forget what i seen. i know it sounds far fetched.
content.summary: 5 to 7 bright lights ascend in to sky n 1 crash

content.detailedDescription: It was a bright day. my friend was going somewhere on his scooter.. he noticed it on the way home.. he told me to get out and see it.. i saw it too but didn't paid lot of attention to it.. the object was stationary. and like it was trying to camouflage in clouds. my friend took the images of it with his mobile phone.. he took two images, one was from an overbridge and the other was from a park.. he sighted it twice.. it was a weird experience.. on that night the moon looked weird.. the moon was surrounded by a white light in a circle.. the moon was centred by that white light.. almost whole of my city noticed it.. we didn't told it to anyone because we thought that people might think we are crazy.

content.detailedDescription:
On 02/24/2016 at approximately 1830 hours i was at work when i looked to the south east and noted that at approximately 30 to 45 degrees there was a bright orange/red colored light in the sky (red arrow in map approximate direction).  as i watched a second light came on just below the first and slightly to the left side, having the same color as the first.  the first light faded out over a couple of seconds leaving the second light.  the process repeated with a third light coming on below the second and to the left.  the second light faded out leaving only the third.  after that there were no further visible lights and the third light faded out leaving no other lights.
  this happened three times over the next 40 minutes approximately.  i recorded one of the occurrences with my cell phone, which does little for detail but shows the pattern of what happened.  i also observed one of the displays through a telescopic rifle scope at 10x power.  no further details were seen even through the scope just bright orange/red lights.  
  later in the evening at approximately 1930 hours i observed a light ascending from the horizon upwards very slowly.  this light was almost straight to the east (indicated by the green arrow on the map) and started very low at about 5 degrees.  the light moved slowly upwards over the next 30 or 40 minutes finally stopping at about 20 to 30 degrees up.  this light had about the same color as the dropping lights. i also watched this light through my rifle scope however as before no further details were identified.  as i watched it it appeared to dim and go out but then come back up again after a few seconds.
  i had no way to tell the distance of the objects from my location (circled in red) however i would estimate they were at least a mile away or more.  these lights were also observed by three other people there with me, and another friends cousin also saw the same light from inside el dorado.  
  in the direction of the east clouds were building up and starting to obscure stars and other details in the sky.  it is possible that these clouds prevented me from seeing any other lights in the distance however i did not believe that the original lights had been high enough in the sky to be covered by ordinary cloud cover.  a helicopter was observed flying in the area briefly before the lights were observed and during the observation of the dropping lights.  i could not see any planes in the area while watching these lights.  the dropping lights could have been military flares, and seemed to be very similar to the phoenix lights video.  mcconnell afb is in wichita and one of the witnesses told me that the planes from mcconnell use unoccupied areas in next door greenwood county for "testing" or training  i have never heard of this happening before, but regardless the direction was not right from were he said this had happened in greenwood county.  i have also not ever observed military craft using flares or other ordinance in the general wichita area.
content.summary: Observed lights dropping towards the se.

content.detailedDescription: I was coming home at 8:30 pm, when i got to my house and looked up i noticed these orbs. i watched them for about 20 minutes before i went inside. my wife said they were stars, and next day i guessed she was right. when i finally zoomed into the pictures on my iphone on noticed the shapes werent round and seemed to have changed shape and direction. the one on the lower left kind of seemed to move down slightly and blink on and off. i also thought i may have seen another one to the left and lower that was moving. the one on the top right has a strange shape. maybe this is just some effect on my iphone? when i was looking at them they seemed round. sorry for the profanity on the videos, i was kind of drunk. note, the are 2 big streetlights on the lower left, glare from a house light on the upper right, and a moth flitting about in one of the videos. the ufos are east / southeast of kodaira, tokyo looking towards koganei.
content.summary: Two lights in the sky, the one on the lower left blinked in an out a few time...In one of the videos there is a moth flying around, not a ufo

content.detailedDescription:
I was sitting on the floor of my basement watching tv when i happened to glance into a mirror (beside the tv) opposite the large window behind me that looked out into my backyard. there, i saw a large head with two huge, angular black eyes. when i looked behind me, i saw nothing outside, but i could see a reflection of the face in the window when i looked at it through the mirror. at first, i thought it was a trick of the light, but when it tilted its head slightly, i knew it wasn't caused by anything in my room, as i had the tv turned off now and i was alone. i was so terrified, all i could do was sit and stare at it through the mirror and back into the window behind me. i could see that it blinked several times as i watched it. after about 30 seconds of having a fight or flight response of just freezing, i finally worked up the courage to bolt out of the room and run upstairs, where my family was already asleep. since i was too scared to stick around long enough (i don't think i've ever been that scared in my life), i never actually saw it leave.
i'm sitting in the same place where i saw it a couple nights ago (nothing has changed position in the basement room like lights or anything) and i see absolutely nothing in the corner of my window. i took out a measuring tape the next morning and measured to where i remembered its head being, and found that it was about 4 feet tall, maybe a little shorter.
normally, the curtains to the window are closed completely, and when i'd be down in the basement by myself with the curtains closed, i would hear what sounded like movement outside. oddly, our motion sensor light didn't come on that night i saw it, though, and the sensor is only a couple feet away from where i saw the entity. for the past several weeks, with the curtains closed, i would be in the basement late at night and alone, watching netflix or tv. however, i would hear strange noises outside like movement, or even tapping on the window. until i saw this entity, i never really took notice or thought these sounds were odd or out of place, as we often have deer, raccoons, rabbits, outdoor cats, and other animals in our backyard. i always assumed the noises were just animals, but now i hesitate to enter the basement at night now that we took the curtains down entirely to replace them.
content.summary: I was sitting in my basement when i saw a short being peering inside the corner of my window. it looked like a grey alien.

content.detailedDescription:

content.detailedDescription: Six of us were outside eating dinner approximately 6pm, just before the sky started darkening. one friend noticed a light and we all looked. at first we thought it was a radio tower light, but then noticed the actual radio tower was a bit lower (it did not align with the tower). near a cloud there was three linear  lights and one blinking light above the three. it moved up and further, disappeared, then reappeared more to the right above another cloud, then disappeared again right away, possibly in the larger cloud. the larger cloud expanded over a large distance in the sky. after it disappeared there was a tremendous amount of fog. we had neutral feelings before the sighting and was anxious and excited after the sighting.
content.summary: We were eating dinner in our college cafeteria and we saw lights hovering in place

content.detailedDescription:
While watching tv i noticed a large object hovering still over the top of one of the mounts in the la national forrest, the morning sky was just starting to light up with the sun rising in the east behind the object, but the sun hadn’t peaked over the mountain just yet. the object caught my attention since it was the only object in the sky; at first i thought this was only a cloud, however there wasn’t any other clouds in the sky.  i took a couple photos and then sat back down on the couch continuing watching tv but still keeping an eye out the window when all of a sudden 5 or 10 minutes later the image moved a bit and had looked like it broke up showing other objects hovering below and to the sides of the larger object; that’s when i confirmed to myself its only a cloud since it had broke up a bit.. but then what happened next is when i realized it’s a ufo.., the object came together as one again and started to leave; it moved east away from where i was.

 

after the ufo left i noticed the morning sky filled with more then a dozen fighter jets.

 

about 1 hour later around 0730 the object repapered; the ufo was cloaked and appeared as a large cloud; next there were 2 fighter jets which flew over our house and headed east toward the ufo.. as the jets approached, the ufo started to leave and head east away from the incoming jets pursuing it; in the distance i noticed what looked like the first jet to plummet down (as if the jet was shoot down or it pursued a drone or something). the scale of how large the ufo was enormous, in the pictures you can tell that the size of the jets in comparison were tiny, this ufo dwarfed our jets, this was their mother ship as its referred to or a floating city.

 

one hour later the object reappeared and headed west toward our house and then north and dropped down behind the mountain ridge. in the distance you could see jets flying all around in that direction. further i saw another plan flying overhead, this was a radar plan, the plan with the large circle dome on the top of it. 

 

there was a lot of activity over the los angeles national forest this morning; i called the news station and the la national ranger station, but no one followed back up with me. 

let me know once you have read this and if you're still interested and want to proceed with a good story i'll give you the photos..

thank you & regards
content.summary: Very large ufo disc observed hovering over mountain top in santa clarita, early morning of 1-14-16
